text: Andrea Parenti is an Italian archer. He was born on 26 April 1965. Parenti competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics, 1992 Summer Olympics, and 1996 Summer Olympics.Andrea ParentiAndrea PARENTI == References == Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Italian archers Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Italy Category:Sportspeople from Emilia-Romagna
